com.shc.ahttp.client.response

Class AHttpClientResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.shc.ahttp.client.response.AHttpClientResponse
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SClientResponse

    public class AHttpClientResponse
extends Object
    This class provides all the fields required to represent the state and content of the response returned from a successful HTTP client call.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.0 $
    Author:
